<header class="sht-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sht-header-titles">
      <h1 class="title">커뮤니티 생성</h1>
      <p class="subtitle is-6">커뮤니티를 생성하여 나만의 게시판을 만들거나, 사람들과 소통할 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<section class="sht-create-wrap">
  <form id="createCommunityForm" action="/api/community" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="put"/>
    <div class="field">
      <label class="label">커뮤니티 이름</label>
      <div class="control">
        <input class="input" type="text" name="comm_name" id="comm_name">
      </div>
      <p>커뮤니티 이름은 최대 20자입니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label class="label">커뮤니티 ID</label>
      <div class="control has-icons-left">
        <input class="input" type="text" name="comm_id" id="comm_id">
        <span class="icon is-medium is-left">
          c/
        </span>
      </div>
      <p>커뮤니티 ID는 알파벳 대/소문자, 숫자, 언더바(_)를 포함할 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <label class="label">커뮤니티 소개</label>
      <div class="control">
        <textarea class="textarea" name="description" id="comm_description"></textarea>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control">
      <button type="submit" class="button is-link is-fullwidth">생성하기</button>
    </div>
  </form>
</section>
